~ ASCIIFY ~

A set of simple tools for turning strings/files into individual ascii chars and vice versa.

This project is meant to teach me how to write GNU-coreutils like code in C using the GNU GPL license and the standard GNU toolset `gcc`, `autoconf`, `automake` and `make`.

Use this for educational purposes only.

* Building:

$ mkdir build && cd build
$ autoreconf -i ../configure.ac
$ ../configure
$ make

* Running:

$ src/asciify
$ src/unasciify

* Installing:

# make install
